      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――雑誌の打ち合わせ中",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――During the magazine meeting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』ですか！？\nわ～！　kana、この企画大好きなんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Miracle☆Idol Birthday!”?!\nWow~! I love that project!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルが誕生日にやりたいことを叶えてくれる、雑誌\nの名物企画ですよね。いつか出たいなって思ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s that famous project in the magazine where idols get to fulfill\ntheir birthday wishes‚ right? I’ve always wanted to be on it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8666655303
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "（……って表向きには言っといてやるけどさぁ）\n（誕生日ギリギリでオファーとか、なんなの？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…That’s what I’ll tell them‚ at least.）\n（What’s with this last-minute birthday offer?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.6333335957
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "（急にやりたいことなんて思いつかないし。それに）\n（「他にも誰か呼んで、誌面を華やかにしたい」？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I can’t think of anything I want to do on such short notice. Besides‚）\n（“We’d like to invite some other people to make the article more interesting”?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4000000716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（はあ……呼べって言うなら、テキトーに呼ぶけど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Sigh… If they want me to invite someone‚ I’ll just invite randomly.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.5999986094,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（引き立て役にぴったりで、暇そうなアイドルか……あ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Someone perfect as a supporting role… an idle-looking idol… Ah!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.0666667383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.099998355
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_51_01-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "決めました！　kana、お誕生日は大好きなスリクス\nのメンバーと過ごしたいです！　具体的には――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve decided! For my birthday‚ I want to spend time with my beloved ⅢX\nmembers! To be more specific――",
